Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:284380,287890}Then what's the point of this training?{NOTE:ではこの過酷な修業の意味は何なのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.97,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:287890,290970}You must've misunderstood what I meant by "strength".{NOTE:強さを誤解しとるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:55.94,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:290970,295940}Your friends are coming here, so let's clear things up together.{NOTE:お前たちの仲間も来てるから一緒に説明してやるだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.06,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:295940,297060}Friends?{NOTE:仲間？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:298690,300940}Oh! It's you guys!{NOTE:おお！みんな～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.45,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:300940,304450}– Hey, Lu—\N– It's been so long!{NOTE:—やあリュー…うわ！\\N—久しぶりだな！ハハハハ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:307280,308780}This takes me back!{NOTE:懐かしい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:308780,311040}I can smell Hakum village on you!{NOTE:ハクム村のにおいがする！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.62,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:312250,313620}O…kay?{NOTE:えっ…そう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.12,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:313620,316120}Long time no see!{NOTE:久しぶりなのだ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:320170,322130}– Mille!\N– Eh?{NOTE:—ミル～！\\N—ひっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.51,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:323550,325510}What's gotten into you? You're creeping me out!{NOTE:何よもう！うっとうしい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:325510,327260}Don't be like that.{NOTE:そう言うなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:327260,330470}Let me smell Hakum village on you!{NOTE:ハクム村のにおいを嗅がせろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.27,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:331560,333270}Don't sniff me!{NOTE:嗅ぐなー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:333270,334770}Floof!{NOTE:チャモ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.48,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:334770,337480}You're annoying-nyaa.{NOTE:うっとうしいでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.94,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:337480,338940}You really are! Geez!{NOTE:ホントよ！もう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:338940,340610}Sorry, sorry.{NOTE:ごめんごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:46.74,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:340610,346740}I've been training ever since I got to the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:いやぁ、タルジュ雪原に来てからさ、こいつと２人でずっと修業ばっかりしてたから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.99,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:346740,349990}So I've been missing you guys like crazy.{NOTE:もうみんなが懐かしくて懐かしくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.70,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:349990,353700}Day after day, I only had Lute's face to look at.{NOTE:毎日毎日見るのはリュートの顔ばかりだったから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.87,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:353700,355870}I've missed you, I've missed you…{NOTE:みんなが恋しくて恋しくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.92,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:355870,357920}Stop licking me-nyaa…{NOTE:やめるでしゅニャ…ハァ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.92,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:362800,364920}But why are you here?{NOTE:だけどみんなどうしてここに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.09,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:365670,369090}We had a fight with Ebon Riders too.\NIt's been tough back home.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズと戦いになって大変だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.47,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:369090,373470}So we decided to try to learn about\Nthe Rite of Channeling too.{NOTE:それで僕たちも伝承の儀を何とか身に付けようと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.10,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:373470,377100}It's not a matter of acquiring knowledge.{NOTE:身に付けるというものでもないダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.56,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:377100,380560}It's about the Channeling Gems I gave you.{NOTE:お前たちに渡したこの絆珠にな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.44,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:380560,383440}And about how to load a Monstie's power into them.{NOTE:…モンスターとの絆を込めるだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.74,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:383440,388740}And also how to use it to awaken the sleeping kinship power within your Monsties.{NOTE:そしてその絆の力を自分のオトモンに目覚めさせるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.95,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:388740,389950}The Gems, huh?{NOTE:これに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.16,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:389950,391160}What does it mean?{NOTE:どういうこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.99,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:391160,393990}It means something like this. Behold!{NOTE:見よ！こういうことなのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.96,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:399210,399960}Oh?{NOTE:あれ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.13,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:399960,402130}It smells kind of sweet…?{NOTE:何だかいいにおいが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:46.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:402130,406130}I've eaten donuts just in case.{NOTE:こんなこともあろうかとさっきドーナツを食べておいたのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:50.34,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:406130,410340}But how can Navirou fart like a Congalala?{NOTE:でも何でナビルーがババコンガみたいなおならをするのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.93,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:410340,413930}It's because I was taught Congalala's power against my will.{NOTE:これが不本意ながら身に付けたババコンガの力だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.22,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:413930,416220}It smells sweet-nyaa.{NOTE:甘～いにおいでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.39,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:416220,418390}How surprising.{NOTE:これは驚きゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:01.60,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:418390,421600}The smell depends on what I ate.{NOTE:においとか効果は食べた物しだいなのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.40,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:421600,424400}We figured it out during our training.{NOTE:リュートとの修業中に目覚めたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.65,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:424400,427650}It smells sweet… but it's still a fart.{NOTE:においは甘いけどおならに変わりないゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.57,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:427650,428570}Yeah.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.95,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:428570,429950}Actually…{NOTE:実は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:429950,433370}Navirou probably doesn't need such power.{NOTE:ナビルー的にはこの力は合っていないと思うのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.74,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:433990,436740}Can we undo this Rite?{NOTE:外す…みたいなことはできないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.95,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:436740,437950}Nope.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.08,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:437950,441080}Can't be done.{NOTE:そういうふうにはならねえだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:25.92,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:441080,445920}Once a kinship with a Monstie has been formed, it can't be broken.{NOTE:一度結んだモンスターとの絆ダ。大事に使え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.51,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:445920,447510}Nya…{NOTE:ニャー…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.76,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:447510,450760}So you can get a Monstie to use different powers…?{NOTE:オトモンがいろんな力を使えるようになるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:37.14,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:450760,457140}So that was the reason why the Ebon Riders' Monsties could use all sorts of attacks?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズのオトモンが本来使えない能力を使ったのはそういうことだったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.77,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:457140,459770}It'd be awesome if my Legion could learn a Breath!{NOTE:レギオンがブレス吐いたらすごそう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:43.60,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:459770,463600}Just be aware that you can't have everything.{NOTE:何でもかんでもというわけにはいかねえダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:48.99,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:463600,468990}There are lots of powers, some are compatible and some that aren't. Choose carefully.{NOTE:合うとか合わねえとか色々だからよく考えて使うだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.11,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:468990,470110}All right.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.86,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:470110,471860}But Dede Geezer…{NOTE:だけどデデ爺。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:55.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:471860,475660}Why did you tell me to train?{NOTE:だったら何で俺修業しなくちゃならなかったんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.08,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:475660,477080}Oh, that's because…{NOTE:お前な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:03.00,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:477080,483000}If you aren't strong enough, strong monsters won't lend you their strength.{NOTE:お前が強くなければ強いモンスターは力を貸してくれねえべよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.88,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:483000,486880}You see, monsters need to acknowledge you.{NOTE:モンスターがお前を認めてくれるかどうかダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.80,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:486880,487800}Oh…{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:13.09,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:488630,493090}So that's what you meant by training to become strong?{NOTE:修業して強くなれってそういうことだったのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.51,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:493090,494510}Yup.{NOTE:そうダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.18,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:494510,497180}Strength isn't just about physical power.{NOTE:強さは力だけではねえんダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:18.93,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:498350,498930}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:26.90,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:500560,506900}But Dede Geezer, how do we put\Na monster's power in the Channeling Gem?{NOTE:だがデデ爺…この絆珠にモンスターの力を込めるというのはどういうふうにやるのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.36,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:506900,510360}Once you meet a monster,\Nyou'll know when the time's right.{NOTE:そりゃあモンスターを前にしたら分かるだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.53,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:510360,511530}Hm.{NOTE:ふむ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:511530,514820}Which strong monster should we bond with?{NOTE:強いモンスターというとどれだろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.83,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:514820,517830}Monsters from around Mount Celion\Nshould be pretty strong.{NOTE:セリオン山のモンスターが強いはずゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:41.16,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:517830,521160}I don't know-nyaa.{NOTE:僕はよく分からないでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.04,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:521160,525040}But I'm not sure if venturing into such a dangerous area is a good idea.{NOTE:でもいきなり危険な場所はどうかと思うけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.25,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:525040,526250}Come on, Hyoro.{NOTE:ちょっとヒョロ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.88,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:526250,527880}Be a little more positive.{NOTE:もっと前向きでいってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.79,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:527880,528790}We're going.{NOTE:行こうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.88,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:528790,529880}Eh?{NOTE:え～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.21,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:529880,531210}Don't "eh?" me here!{NOTE:｢え～｣じゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.59,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:531210,532590}Ehh…?{NOTE:え～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:533670,535090}What do we do, Lute?{NOTE:どうする？リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:536180,537260}I…{NOTE:俺は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:538010,541600}There's a monster I'd like to meet again if I'm to be awarded with power.{NOTE:力を授かるならもう一度会いたいモンスターがいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.56,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:542100,543560}You mean Congalala?{NOTE:ババコンガ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.27,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:543560,545270}Heck no!{NOTE:違う！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.74,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:552530,556740}I see you still haven't gotten Lute's Kinship Stone.{NOTE:まだリュートの絆石は手に入らぬのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.49,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:556740,559490}We're terribly sorry, Master Anvis.{NOTE:申し訳ありませんアンヴィスさま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:24.62,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:559490,564620}Ever since Gale let him go, we haven't been able to locate him.{NOTE:このゲイルめが取り逃がして以来やつの行方は分からないのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.25,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:564620,566250}Hey! Are you blaming it on me?{NOTE:えっ！俺のせい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:566250,567920}It's not my fault.{NOTE:そりゃないっすよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:567920,571050}You all went to Hakum village too.{NOTE:先輩たちもハクム村に行ってるんすから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.84,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:571050,573840}But you were the first one who lost.{NOTE:最初に逃がしたお前が悪い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:573840,576130}Ah, so it's all my fault.{NOTE:っす…俺が悪いっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.30,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:576130,579300}Then take responsibility for it.{NOTE:悪いと思うなら責任取ってよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:579300,582520}Of course. As soon as we know his location.{NOTE:やつの居場所が分かればすぐにでも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.68,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:582520,584680}Kinship Ore.{NOTE:絆原石だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.85,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:584680,586850}Kinship Ore…?{NOTE:絆原石？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:51.57,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:586850,591570}Lute is the Rider that purified the Kinship Ore.{NOTE:リュートは絆原石を浄化してきたライダーだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:56.24,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:591570,596240}So the possibility is high that he'll seek it again.{NOTE:再びその地を訪れていても不思議はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.99,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:596240,598990}There are seven Kinship Ores, aren't there?{NOTE:絆原石７つあるんですよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.66,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:598990,600660}That's correct.{NOTE:そのとおり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:05.08,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:600660,605080}So let's decide between the four of us\Nwho will go and search for him.{NOTE:ではわれら四天王で分担を決めて探しに行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.25,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:605080,606250}Sounds good.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.08,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:606250,608080}It'll make our chances equal.{NOTE:チャンスは平等に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.40,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:633610,635400}Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:635400,638650}I don't think that monster's here anymore.{NOTE:もうあのモンスターは現れないと思うぞ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.07,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:638650,640070}You think…?{NOTE:どうだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.20,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:640070,643200}I guess it does look different from when we purified it.{NOTE:あのときとは状況が違うし…}
